==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Restful
<hw>Rest"ful</hw> <pr>(r?st"f?l)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Being at rest; quiet.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Giving rest; freeing from toil, trouble,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Tired with all these, for <qex>restful</qex> death I cry.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Rest"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Rest"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rest-harrow</ent>⟦br⟧
